latestPosts.caption:
Introducing our esteemed judge for Panache ( Modelling) Ms.Muskaan Batra. Winner of the Miss Internet Popular award in Miss Navi Mumbai 2022, Muskaan is a well-trained actor from the Kishore Namit Kapoor acting institute. She has played the role of "Nikki" in Sufiyana Pyaar Mera on Star Bharat and worked in the Zee TV reality show "Apka Sapna Hamara Apna." Muskaan has been a content creator for various renowned brands over the past four years, including fashion and beauty brands. 

With three years of experience in real estate modeling, she has worked on 350+ projects in Mumbai and Navi Mumbai. Her impressive portfolio includes performing with Kapil Sharma, working in Marathi films as a dancer, and performing on stage shows. Muskaan is a trained dancer in Bollywood, hip hop, freestyle, and bollyhip. She is confident and passionate about her journey as an actor and model.
